des: A collection of short form audio updates weekly (The Tailwind Digital Minute) uncovering news headlines from Google, Facebook, Bing, and more. Hear your hosts, Ryan Gudmundson, David Ericson, Leslie DeMent, Priscilla Plazola, and more every week from the Tailwind offices in Tempe, AZ
